====The impact outweighs—key to respond to all major global challenges====
Christian O. Lundberg 10 Professor of Communications @ University of North Carolina, Chapel Hill, &amp;#34;Tradition of Debate in North Carolina&amp;#34; in Navigating Opportunity: Policy Debate in the 21st Century By Allan D. Louden, p. 311

