Ilex Associates, 96 – Consultants to the British Department of Trade and Industry (&amp;#34;A REVIEW OF OVERSEAS FINANCING MECHANISMS AND INCENTIVES FOR COMMERCIAL RENEWABLE ENERGY PROJECTS&amp;#34;, http://www.berr.gov.uk/files/file15101.pdf-http://www.berr.gov.uk/files/file15101.pdf)

