Knops 2007 – DPhil, Lecturer, Department of Political Science and International Studies, University of Birmingham, UK (March, Andrew, Journal of Political Philosophy, 15.1, &amp;#34;Debate: Agonism as Deliberation – On Mouffe~’s Theory of Democracy&amp;#34;, Wiley Online)

